<h2>Why Crude Oil Price Affects PP Bags?</h2>

<p>
Polypropylene (PP) is made from petroleum products. This means:
</p>

<ul>
<li>When crude oil price increases → PP raw material price increases</li>
<li>When oil supply is unstable → production cost becomes unpredictable</li>
</ul>

<p>
👉 So directly, <strong>PP bag prices depend on crude oil market</strong>.
</p>

